# Research loop

When running a research / Frontier rotation:

- Only edit `docs/RESEARCH.md` and `docs/BACKLOG.md` (plus tiny related docs clarifications if required)
- Do not write application code, sandboxes, or approach card rewrites mid-research
- Do not promote to a default playbook or “ROADMAP” from research alone
- One research change-set at a time; finish learn notes before stacking another
- Experiments and builds are separate sessions/loops
